---Quote--- 
ROCHESTER, M.N. - The man serving a life sentence in the January...</description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<div><a href="http://www.abc15.com/news/region-central-southern-az/tucson/convicted-killer-jared-loughner-files-25m-lawsuit-against-gabrielle-giffords" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Convicted killer Jared Loughner files $25M lawsuit against Gabrielle Giffords</a><br />
<br />
<div class="bbcode_container">
	<div class="bbcode_description">Quote:</div>
	<div class="bbcode_quote printable">
		<hr />
		
			ROCHESTER, M.N. - The man serving a life sentence in the January 2011 shooting in Tucson that killed six and injured many others, including then-Rep. Gabrielle Giffords, has filed a $25 million lawsuit against her.<br />
<br />
Jared Loughner seeks $25 million in punitive damages against Giffords for &quot;causing me emotion and psychological distress,&quot; according to the March 18 filing .<br />
 <br />
&quot;My incarceration is illegal. I am actually innocent. I was Framed. I am a victim of project mk-ultra the govt. put a chip in my head to control my mind,&quot; Loughner claims.<br />
<br />
Note: Capitalizations, abbreviations, spelling and grammatical errors are reflective of the documents filed.<br />
<br />
Among Loughner's more outlandish claims:<br />
<div style="margin-left:40px">• Giffords is part of the Illuminati<br />
• She &quot;never got shot, it was all an act,&quot; she learned from watching Ronald Reagan movies<br />
• He's become &quot;sick and delusional&quot; from chemtrails in the sky<br />
• He was &quot;handpicked illegally to be a sleeper assassin&quot;<br />
• He's waterboarded everyday by the NSA, CIA, ATF on Gifford's orders<br />
• She set up &quot;poor man&quot; Cliven Bundy and &quot;infiltrated&quot; the ranch<br />
• She financed the shooters in the deadly San Bernardino shooting<br />
• His attorney framed Dzhokhar Tsarnaev, the man convicted in the Boston Marathon bombings<br />
• He does not get access to NPR or CSPAN</div><br />
The convicted killer sent the filing from Rochester, Minnesota where he is serving his sentence.<br />
<br />
Giffords suffered a gunshot wound to the head and underwent months of treatment because of the shooting.<br />
<br />
